## Constraints & Prohibitions

### PROHIBITED
- ❌ Making changes without git status check
- ❌ Committing without push
- ❌ Leaving uncommitted changes
- ❌ Changing files on wrong branch
- ❌ Mixing English and German in same file
- ❌ Removing existing content without explicit request
- ❌ Using outdated version numbers
- ❌ Duplicating content between files without purpose
- ❌ Changing HTML structure/CSS classes
- ❌ Skip git push—it must complete every workflow

### ALWAYS
- ✅ Check git status first
- ✅ Read existing content before adding
- ✅ Keep consistent formatting
- ✅ Update version numbers
- ✅ Verify all files updated together
- ✅ Push to git after every completed workflow
- ✅ Maintain language consistency per file
- ✅ Validate cross-file consistency

